Property Tax Extension Limitation Law.  As used </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">10</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>in this Division 5:
</code><code>
</code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">11</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code>"Consumer Price Index" means the Consumer Price Index for </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">12</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>All Urban
